{"tid":2190273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[非反送中] 裝修工認藏子彈霰彈槍 篤灰刑期減半囚6年","createTime":"2020-09-05T13:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T14:08:47.000Z","uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ca11a6422b1b08a2053c73335eff66c0daf4d7fc","tid":2190273,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200904/s00046/53dc298cc56e205f43f5614b62699e61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200904%2Fs00046%2F53dc298cc56e205f43f5614b62699e61.jpg&h=ebe2f900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n58歲裝修工前年凌晨在深水埗通州街公園附近被<span class=\"red\"><strong>搜出一支已上子彈的霰彈槍及7發子彈</strong></span>，聲稱替他人保管涉案槍彈，<strong><span class=\"red\">被捕當日因女友人稱男朋友遇襲而帶槍借她</span></strong>，早前承認無牌管有槍械及彈藥罪，昨在高等法院判刑。法官李素蘭考慮被告第一時間認罪，以及轉為污點證人成功頂證給他子彈的另一被告，扣減他一半刑期，判監6年3個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳東荣（58歲），承認於2018年7月21日在深水埗無牌管有一支霰彈槍及7發子彈。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時稱，會將量刑起點訂為12年，惟<strong><span class=\"red\">被告從內地偷運槍及子彈來港，涉及跨境犯罪，並明知女友人會將槍用作犯罪用途下借槍給她，被捕時霰彈槍亦已上膛，以上均屬加刑因素</span></strong>，因此加刑半年。<br />\n<br />\n法官考慮被告第一時間認罪，涉案槍械並無使用過，被捕後一直主動與警方合作，且提供真實而重要證供指證另一被告，將其成功定罪，故接納辯方求情理由，扣減一半刑期，最終判監6年3個月。<br />\n<br />\n案情稱，警員當晚巡邏時看見不斷徘徊的被告，上前截查時被告拔足逃跑，最終被截停並搜出一支已上膛的霰彈槍，警員沿被告的逃跑路線再發現另外6發子彈。陳在警誡下聲稱代人保管槍械及彈藥，被捕當日因女友人說她的男友被人襲擊，應其要求才帶槍借給她。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200904/s00002/1599157185289/%e8%a3%9d%e4%bf%ae%e5%b7%a5%e8%aa%8d%e8%97%8f%e5%ad%90%e5%bd%88%e9%9c%b0%e5%bd%88%e6%a7%8d-%e7%af%a4%e7%81%b0%e5%88%91%e6%9c%9f%e6%b8%9b%e5%8d%8a%e5%9b%9a6%e5%b9%b4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200904%2Fs00002%2F1599157185289%2F%25e8%25a3%259d%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e8%25aa%258d%25e8%2597%258f%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%25bd%2588%25e9%259c%25b0%25e5%25bd%2588%25e6%25a7%258d-%25e7%25af%25a4%25e7%2581%25b0%25e5%2588%2591%25e6%259c%259f%25e6%25b8%259b%25e5%258d%258a%25e5%259b%259a6%25e5%25b9%25b4&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=82496950\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200904%2Fs00002%2F1599157185289%2F%25e8%25a3%259d%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e8%25aa%258d%25e8%2597%258f%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%25bd%2588%25e9%259c%25b0%25e5%25bd%2588%25e6%25a7%258d-%25e7%25af%25a4%25e7%2581%25b0%25e5%2588%2591%25e6%259c%259f%25e6%25b8%259b%25e5%258d%258a%25e5%259b%259a6%25e5%25b9%25b4&h=9e487bd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200904/s00002/1599157185289/%e8%a3%9d%e4%bf%ae%e5%b7%a5%e8%aa%8d%e8%97%8f%e5%ad%90%e5%bd%88%e9%9c%b0%e5%bd%88%e6%a7%8d-%e7%af%a4%e7%81%b0%e5%88%91%e6%9c%9f%e6%b8%9b%e5%8d%8a%e5%9b%9a6%e5%b9%b4</a>"},{"pid":"d61e1e6a6e04cd64c1b781ecfe02fa0d764f5c93","tid":2190273,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"orange\">第238章 《火器及彈藥條例》<br />\n13.無牌管有槍械或彈藥</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(1) 任何人除非持有槍械或彈藥的管有權牌照或經營人牌照，否則不得管有該等槍械或彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n(2) 任何人違反第(1)款，即屬犯罪，一經循公訴程序定罪，可處第6級罰款及<strong><span class=\"orange\">監禁14年</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"279e503d51ad79b56501b9b474d9a5a8ff5fd284","tid":2190273,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"12年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4f81417fd34929097673a769d6905559e2fd3c","tid":2190273,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"黑警唔帶罩？"},{"pid":"792bf9824809ff97f330c315115a036f545c8580","tid":2190273,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"帶支自拍棍仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cd9d08036e8cc8e85d61bd3420209ba6cb03cc","tid":2190273,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike